---
title: Southern Pork Chops with Collard Green-Potato Hash and Black Pepper Gravy
description: A bit of seasoned flour is the secret to getting a perfectly golden sear on these pork chops. Crispy roasted potatoes and earthy collard greens are tossed together for a delicious hash. A creamy black pepper gravy ties it all together. For best results, use freshly ground black pepper.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/southern-pork-chops-90146309.jpg
